reviewText: I WAS LOOKING FOR 2 SEPARATE MOVIES: 1)  "ASTEROID"  AND  2) "DOOMSDAY ROCK".  I WOULD LIKE TO GET THESE ON DVD AND  IN ENGLISH FOR REGION 1 ALSO.  WHAT I ENDED UP WITH WAS A DOCUMENTARY CALLED:  "ASTEROID; THE DOOMSDAY ROCK"--NOT WHAT I WANTED.
I wanted Doomsday Rock with Connie Selleca.  BUT IT ISN'T ON DVD.
